            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ex edictu <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Cor<lb break="no" n="2"/>neli Dolabel<expan><ex>la</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> le<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>pro <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> determin<supplied reason="lost">avit</supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex cert="low">purius</ex></expan> Titius Geminus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>pri</abbr><ex>nceps</ex></expan> posterior <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>VII inter Neditas <lb n="7"/>et Corinienses <lb n="8"/>restituti iussu <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Duceni Gemini <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> Augusti <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> p<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="11"/>per <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulum</ex></expan> Resium <supplied reason="lost">M</supplied>a<lb break="no" n="12"/>ximum |(centurionem) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>incipem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>posterior</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/>et <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintum</ex></expan> Aebutium <lb n="15"/>Liberalem <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>astat</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="16"/><expan><abbr>posteriore</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="17"/>eiusdem
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Höhe bezieht sich auf den sichtbaren Teil über der Erde. Z. 2 (Ende) und Z. 3 (Ende) Buchstaben G bzw. AV bei der Auffindung noch lesbar. Z. 4 (Anfang): möglicherweise auch S mit nur aufgemalter Querhaste für S(extus). (B): Abramić - Colnago; CIL III 9973; ILS; Wilkes; ILJug: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
